OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714286
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FBristol Airport has submitted plans to
OL,7,Fextend both its runway and terminal
OL,8,Fsaying it will create jobs and boost
OL,9,Fthe economy in the area.
OL,11,FIf approved, the proposals could see
OL,12,Fmore destinations offered to
OL,13,Ftravellers from Bristol Airport
OL,14,Fincluding long-haul flights to North
OL,15,FAmerica and the Middle East.
OL,17,FThe airport says the plans, first
OL,18,Fannounced in 2024, would create 1,000
OL,19,Fon-site jobs and invest #500 million
OL,20,Finto the airport and local
OL,21,Finfrastructure.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714286
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FBut campaigners say the plans would
OL,7,Fput too much pressure on local roads
OL,8,Fand threaten the wellbeing of people
OL,9,Fliving nearby.
OL,11,F"Our proposals deliver what customers
OL,12,Fhave told us they want to see at their
OL,13,Flocal Airport," said Dave Lees, Chief
OL,14,FExecutive of Bristol Airport.
OL,16,F"There is an incredible amount of
OL,17,Feconomic investment in the West of
OL,18,FEngland and it's an exciting time for
OL,19,Fthe region with so much opportunity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714286
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,F"At Bristol Airport we have a
OL,7,Fresponsibility to meet that level of
OL,8,Fambition and ensure we have an Airport
OL,9,Fthat connects our region and meets
OL,10,Fdemand from a growing population for
OL,11,Fair travel."
OL,13,FThe airport says the plans would see
OL,14,Faround #500 million invested in
OL,15,Fimprovements at the airport and local
OL,16,Finfrastructure.
OL,26,@sD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
