FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714287
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FThese include extending the runway to
OL,7,Faccommodate larger aircraft and
OL,8,Fincreasing capacity of the terminal
OL,9,Fand the ability to walk onto aircraft
OL,10,Fwithout getting on a bus.
OL,12,FAs part of the plans, the Airport is
OL,13,Fapplying for permission to increase
OL,14,Fthe current passenger cap of 12
OL,15,Fmillion passengers per annum to 15
OL,16,Fmillion passengers per annum, which it
OL,17,Fexpects to reach in the late 2030s.
OL,18,FCurrently 10.8 million people use
OL,19,FBristol Airport.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714287
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FAircraft movements would increase from
OL,7,F85,990 to 100,000 per year in the
OL,8,Flonger term to meet demand for air
OL,9,Ftravel. On a busy day in peak period
OL,10,Fthis would result in 35 extra aircraft
OL,11,Fmovements.
OL,13,FWhile night flying restrictions would
OL,14,Fremain, the Airport is proposing to
OL,15,Fincrease night flights by 1,000 per
OL,16,Fyear - on average, four per night on a
OL,17,Fbusy night in the peak period.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
