FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714287
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FBristol Airport says it has worked
OL,7,Fclosely with airlines to improve the
OL,8,Ftype of aircraft operating from the
OL,9,FAirport. It says it has actively
OL,10,Fencouraged quieter new engine option
OL,11,Faircrafts, which have a 50% reduction
OL,12,Fin noise compared to standard aircraft.
OL,14,FThe extension of the airport's runway
OL,15,Fwould encroach on Felton Common, a 100-
OL,16,Facre green space owned by Winford
OL,17,FParish Council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714287
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FThe Save Felton Common group said a
OL,7,Frecent consultation received 640
OL,8,F"universally negative" comments about
OL,9,Fthe proposed expansion onto the
OL,10,FCommon, which would see 3-metre high
OL,11,Ffencing and 8.5 metre-tall lights put
OL,12,Fup.
OL,14,FOther campaigners have expressed
OL,15,Fconcern about the impact on local
OL,16,Froads.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
