FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714287
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,F"Local people and current airport
OL,7,Fcustomers are already experiencing
OL,8,Freal problems with a congested A38 and
OL,9,Fsurrounding network of smaller roads,"
OL,10,Fsaid Richard Baxter from Bristol
OL,11,FAirport Action Network.
OL,13,F"There is much talk and speculation
OL,14,Fabout a mass transport system but it's
OL,15,Fgoing to be a really expensive
OL,16,Fchallenge which will take at least a
OL,17,Fdecade to complete.
OL,19,F"Meanwhile, the local road network and
OL,20,Fthe largely single tracked A38 is
OL,21,Fgoing to be overwhelmed by traffic."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
