PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774714287
OL,3,CCampaigners concerned as airport
OL,4,Csubmits plans for major expansion
OL,6,FBristol Airport is already undergoing
OL,7,Fa #400 million upgrade which has
OL,8,Fincluded the construction of a new
OL,9,FPublic Transport Interchange.
OL,11,FThe proposals are expected to be
OL,12,Fposted on North Somerset Council's
OL,13,Fwebsite within the next fortnight.
OL,15,FLocal people and organisations will
OL,16,Fhave the opportunity to submit
OL,17,Fcomments for the council to consider
OL,18,Fbefore it makes its decision later
OL,19,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
